874 A.2d 410 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND, Petitioner, v. David A. WEISKOPF, Respondent. Misc. Docket AG No. 67,

Sept. Term, 2004.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. May 10, 2004.

ORDER

This matter came before the Court on the Joint Petition for Placement on Inactive Status. Upon consideration of the said petition, it is this 10th day of May, 2004,

ORDERED, that the Respondent David A. Weiskopf, be and he is hereby placed on inactive status until further Order of this Court and, it is further

ORDERED, that the Clerk of this Court shall remove the name of David A. Weiskopf from the register of attorneys in this Court until further Order of this Court and, shall certify that fact to the Client Protection Fund and the Clerks of all judicial tribunals in this State in accordance with Maryland Rule 16-772(d).
